tedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T14:02:14.000Z","msg":"唉，same here"},{"pid":"f7b5dffc255ab435bf4883d1b7b2f031c3ec59a7","tid":144860,"uid":4933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T14:18:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>放過左自己成個人真係會舒服哂<br />\n一開始嗰排係難捱啲<br />\n但之後捱過左就知道自己嘅決定係冇錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nSad but true<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一時的痛苦真係個下，連自信心，自尊心都越來越低，好在時間會慢慢掉淡。<br />\n<br />\n一定係無得還完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a9337786e4a724ac99b3c402d6592bb61c9e174","tid":144860,"uid":66,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T14:19:52.000Z","msg":"Nothing ever happened <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00a40fac420ec0afab39c9d1459e6f1eb7d879ff","tid":144860,"uid":48572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T07:26:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}